      "x": 70,
      "y": 540,
      "width": 1260,
      "height": 55,
      "text": "Celebrity content = millions of views, few leads.  Peptide content = fewer views, but comment:like ratio near 1:1.  Every comment = warm lead into DM automation.\nNAD+ reel: 328 comments / 374 likes = 0.88 ratio   |   Laser reel: 2,033 comments / 4,152 likes = 0.49 ratio   |   Erbium: 921 comments / 1,566 likes = 0.59 ratio\nThis is the lead generation engine. \"Comment [KEYWORD] and I'll send you more info\" → ManyChat auto-DM → Quiz/Booking link → Email capture → Patient",
