    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "hooks-body",
      "x": 70,
      "y": 1158,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "CURIOSITY GAP (highest reach):\n  \"[Celebrity]'s eyes look nothing like they did a few years ago\"\n  \"There's a molecule in your body that quietly controls how much energy you have\"\n  \"Have you noticed how [Celebrity] looks almost like their [year] self again?\"\n  \"Your body has a built-in defense system most people never think about\"\n\nBOLD CLAIM / PATTERN INTERRUPT:\n  \"Everybody looks the same in 2025\"\n  \"This might look crazy, but it's not skin damage\"\n  \"Don't do skin tightening if you're not willing to let your skin reset\"\n  \"The biggest lips in the world — but at what cost?\"\n\nQUESTION HOOKS:\n  \"Would you trade one week of downtime for skin that looks better all year?\"\n  \"Have you noticed how peptides keep coming up in weight loss conversations?\"\n\nTEMPLATE FORMULAS:\n  \"[Celebrity] changed dramatically — good genetics or [pop culture ref]?\"\n  \"[Treatment] works... until [unexpected limitation]\"\n  \"Stop [common thing] if you're not willing to [trade-off]\"",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CURIOSITY GAP (highest reach):\n  \"[Celebrity]'s eyes look nothing like they did a few years ago\"\n  \"There's a molecule in your body that quietly controls how much energy you have\"\n  \"Have you noticed how [Celebrity] looks almost like their [year] self again?\"\n  \"Your body has a built-in defense system most people never think about\"\n\nBOLD CLAIM / PATTERN INTERRUPT:\n  \"Everybody looks the same in 2025\"\n  \"This might look crazy, but it's not skin damage\"\n  \"Don't do skin tightening if you're not willing to let your skin reset\"\n  \"The biggest lips in the world — but at what cost?\"\n\nQUESTION HOOKS:\n  \"Would you trade one week of downtime for skin that looks better all year?\"\n  \"Have you noticed how peptides keep coming up in weight loss conversations?\"\n\nTEMPLATE FORMULAS:\n  \"[Celebrity] changed dramatically — good genetics or [pop culture ref]?\"\n  \"[Treatment] works... until [unexpected limitation]\"\n  \"Stop [common thing] if you're not willing to [trade-off]\"",
