    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "funnel-body",
      "x": 730,
      "y": 1158,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "REEL posted (reach: 10-100K views)\n    ↓ Viewer comments keyword (e.g. \"NAD+\")\nMANYCHAT DM AUTOMATION ($15/mo)\n    ↓ Auto-sends quiz link or peptide guide\nLEAD MAGNET — \"Which Peptide Is Right For You?\" quiz\n    ↓ Captures email + phone number\nEMAIL NURTURE SEQUENCE (3-5 emails)\n    ↓ Education → social proof → book consult CTA\nBOOK CONSULT ($0 or $49 intro)\n    ↓ Video call with NP/PA → labs ordered\nRx + PHARMACY SHIPS → Patient onboarded\n    ↓\nSUBSCRIPTION: $299-499/mo recurring\n\nEstimated Conversion Rates:\n  1-3% of reel viewers → comment/lead\n  20-30% of leads → book consult\n  50-70% of consults → become patient\n\nMath: 50K views → 500 comments → 150 leads → 45 consults → 27 patients\n      27 patients x $350/mo = $9,450/mo from ONE viral reel",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "REEL posted (reach: 10-100K views)\n    ↓ Viewer comments keyword (e.g. \"NAD+\")\nMANYCHAT DM AUTOMATION ($15/mo)\n    ↓ Auto-sends quiz link or peptide guide\nLEAD MAGNET — \"Which Peptide Is Right For You?\" quiz\n    ↓ Captures email + phone number\nEMAIL NURTURE SEQUENCE (3-5 emails)\n    ↓ Education → social proof → book consult CTA\nBOOK CONSULT ($0 or $49 intro)\n    ↓ Video call with NP/PA → labs ordered\nRx + PHARMACY SHIPS → Patient onboarded\n    ↓\nSUBSCRIPTION: $299-499/mo recurring\n\nEstimated Conversion Rates:\n  1-3% of reel viewers → comment/lead\n  20-30% of leads → book consult\n  50-70% of consults → become patient\n\nMath: 50K views → 500 comments → 150 leads → 45 consults → 27 patients\n      27 patients x $350/mo = $9,450/mo from ONE viral reel",
